First, the main character finds a fire, then he goes forward and lights two areas. 
After that, he goes further and finds another traveler who tells him that the fire is not infinite and he needs to bring it to a special place to give light to the whole world.
Further on his way there is another area, if he lights it, the fire goes out. 
Further on his way he meets the sea, if he does not enter a word, the boat capsizes and the light goes out. 
When he reaches a special place, if there is fire, then the sun appears, otherwise stars appear
